						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">The scheme used by Guardian Legend is more complicated than that. That game uses DMC IRQs as a timer so that it knows when to update the status bar whenever 64 sprites are to be displayed on the screen without wasting the primary object.</div>
