<br />Really? Well, I didn't look at the game's source or anything, I just noticed that no matter the level there is a strange square in the bottom right. I figured out it was to get a sprite 0 hit at that point.
<br />You mean It uses DMC IRQs *ONLY* when the 64 sprites are being used? I know the game uses a lot of sprites and all, but... going through the trouble of using DMC IRQs to save 1 sprite? That's crazy... The game already flickers like hell (depending mostly on the kind of weapon you shoot), what difference does 1 little sprite make?!</div>

